Ing '''''saṁvega''''' metung yang terminung [[Budista]]ng magindika ning kapanandaman na ning tsoki, pagkadesmáyu at urhensiang espiritual a matakásan ya ing ''[[saṁsāra]]''. Agpang kang [[Ṭhānissaro Bhikkhu]], ini ya "ing primerung emosiong súkat mung dalan king pagsáne [king [[Meditasiong Budista|pámaggúnam]]]".<ref name=degraff2006>https://www.dhammatalks.org/books/Meditations3/Section0013.html</ref>

Importanting e manatílî king estádu ning ''saṁvega'', úli king magresulta ini king [[Niilismu|niilistang]] desesperasion.<ref name=degraff2018>[[Ṭhānissaro Bhikkhu|De Graff, G.]] (2018). [http://www.dhammatalks.org/books/NobleStrategy/Section0004.html Affirming the truths of the heart]. ''Noble strategy''. Mettā Forest Monastery.</ref>

